German Messerschmitt Bf-110 aircraft attack Allied Ground targets. Allied aircraft shot down by Me-109s and antiaircraft fire

Views from inside German Messerschmitt Bf-110 heavy fighters as they fly and attack Allied ground targets with rockets and cannon fire. German ME-109 fighter in flight. Allied aircraft shot down in flames, seen from distance on the ground. A parachute is seen above one. German antiaircraft guns seen. Location: Germany. Date:  1940.
